Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Nancy Reagan's astrologer, 1988
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0440w6f
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 29 May 1988
Former White House aide Donald Regan makes public the First Lady's intrusion on policy and appointments. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less